page.title: 11THE MANOR HOUSE
page.content: 1553....Nicholas Halswell of Goathurst (and Thomas Sydney) Hugh Haswell 1647....Jane, daughter of Hugh Haswell 1648....Colonel, John Tynte (who married John Haswell) 1670....Sir Halswell Tynte 1702....Sir John Tynte 1710....Sir Halswell Tynte 1730....Sir Johne Tynte (rev) 1740....Sir Charles Kemeys-Tynte 1785....Colonel Kemeys-Tynte 1850....Colonel Kemeys-Tynte (John) 1882....Charles Kemeys Kemeys-Tynte 1891....Halswell Milbourne Kemeys-Tynte 1936....LORD WHARTON 1938....BRIDGWATER CORPORATION 1963....WEST SOMERSET WATER BOARD 1963....MICHAEL MARTIN(UNINHABITABLE) 1972....MOVED IN AFTER SOME RENOVATION GRADE TWO LISTED BUILDING.
